Source: skol-gnservices
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Maintainer: La Monte Henry Piggy Yarroll <piggy.yarroll+skol@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), curl, ca-certificates
Standards-Version: 4.6.0
Homepage: https://github.com/piggyatbaqaqi/skol

Package: skol-gnservices
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, adduser
Description: gnfinder + gnparser as local HTTP services for skol
 Bundles the gnfinder and gnparser binaries from the gnames project
 as systemd-managed HTTP services on localhost:9080 and localhost:9081
 respectively.  Skol's v4 span layer (taxon-name detection and
 authorship parsing) connects to these services per-line; running
 them locally avoids round-trip latency and rate-limiting from the
 public globalnames.org API.
 .
 The bundled binaries are statically-linked Go executables released
 by the gnames project under Apache-2.0.  This package fetches the
 release tarballs from github.com/gnames at build time; the
 installed .deb is self-contained.
 .
 Ports + concurrency are tunable via /etc/skol-gnservices/ports.conf.
